description: Deletes the specified certificate associated with the Provisioning Service

certificatenonce.description: Random number generated to indicate Proof of Possession.

provisioning_service_name.description: The name of the provisioning service.

certificatepurpose.description: A description that mentions the purpose of the certificate.

certificate_name.description: This is a mandatory field, and is the logical name of the certificate that the provisioning service will access by.

certificatelast_updated.description: Time the certificate is last updated.

certificatehas_private_key.description: Indicates if the certificate contains a private key.

certificatename.description: This is optional, and it is the Common Name of the certificate.

certificateis_verified.description: Indicates if certificate has been verified by owner of the private key.
